!! Coordination and leadership of many national and international projects, particularly:

* [[CitiObs -- Enhancing Citizen Observatories for healthy, sustainable, resilient and inclusive cities|https://citiobs.eu/]] - EC, Horizon Europe, 1/1/2022 - 31/12/2026. [[NECU|https://necu.org.ua/en]] is a partner of international consortium.
* [[SPARCS -- Sustainable energy Positive & zero cARbon CommunitieS|https://sparcs.info/]] (IA Innovation action) - LC-SC3-SCC-1-2018-2019-2020. Horizon 2020 Framework Programme (H2020). [[NECU|https://necu.org.ua/en]] is a partner of international consortium. Project started in 2019.
* [[AirZOOM - clean air for your child - mobile network of air quality monitoring|https://gb.kyivcity.gov.ua/projects/11/1300]]. Public budget of Kyiv Municipality for 2020, started 2019 - completed 30.12.2020 ([[web-link|https://protw.github.io/airzoom/]]).
